    "1553209440320942007/02/07 07:12:07DaerionThere's really only one tricky bit with this quest, and it's at the fountain in Moonbrook.  Assuming no one else has cleared the area for you you'll see a mob at the cart and a mage at the fountain.  Because the traitor won't stop unless he's engaged in combat, the first mob aggros and runs after him but doesn't stop him until he's in aggro range of the fountain mage.  As soon as the mage hits the traitor, he runs to the fountain and aggros another mage on the other side.  Be ready with poly, sap, a pet, or a friend to stem the tide.",
