    "9595159155101591552007/09/27 02:56:26HyleBit of information on the magewraith. He is a level 10 mage type that seem to cast fireballs, arcane bolts and will sometimes cast a counterspell. He is immune to polymorph since he is undead. The arcane bolts drain 25 mana on top of the damage done. When he is summoned, he says something to the effect of \"Who dares wield magic in my presence\". He despawns after about 30 seconds if not engaged. If you get killed by him and are quick enough you can go back to your body and try again before he dies/despawns. The second part of the \"control\" used in the quest name is making sure you have enough mana after every kill to fight him. Too little and he will drain you and take you out. He never comes into melee so just hit him with everything you have.",
