    "6124175658101756582007/10/27 15:54:55AClockworkLimeIf you're even more morbid, or perhaps looking for an excuse for the blatant murdering of innocents, the cured and strangled carcasses are also skinnable.  Your cursor doesn't change when you hover over them, but if you right-click they still get skinned. :)",
