    "271182986101829862007/11/12 15:39:32AssayeSoloed as a level 18 priest. \
\
tried Foozah's method, died twice. Ended up doing this:\
\
Make sure full mana and health (duh) and buff up. Don't need scrolls, but they are useful. \
\
1) Smite and MB before he gets to you.\
2) Shield\
3) SW:P\
4) dance backwards/sideways out of his way\
5) MB\
6) Shield \
\
7) keep moving out of the way, MBing and renew SW:P and Shield when you have spare mana.\
\
Always heal before you hit 250 hp. He takes health off FAST. And make sure you have at least one health potion for if you time things wrong/go oom.\
\
Good luck!",
