    "9863968610396862007/02/21 03:02:14trizzetI just completed getting the pelts, and the drop rate was 4/9 from the Moonstalker Sires and 1/4 from the Moonstalker Matriarchs.  The biggest problem I had was the slow respawn rate and trying to track them down before other players got to them when they respawned.\
