    "986130955501309552007/08/02 08:47:03taleThere are a lot more Moonstalker Sires and Matriarchs at the far northern edge of the zone, past Mathystra.  If you have this quest when you are doing any of the Mathystra Relics, Tower of Althalaxx, or Gyromast quests, then doing the moonstalkers up north is very close by and rarely in competition with other players.   (In doing this quest on several alts, I've never ever seen someone else up there.)",
    "986142972201429722007/08/23 17:33:51blackoutI found this quest to be a total pain in the butt in the south so I went up north to do it. I found a great area at [59.8, 11.4] there are so many of the buggers there you have to try hard not to get adds. Also pick up the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=951]Mathystra Relics[/url] quest as you can pick up the items right around this same area.\
