    "9861431521201431522007/08/24 01:07:43VelamatuThis quest can be a menace. Here are a few tips:\
 This quest has an unpredictable drop rate. Typically a bad one.\
 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=2237]Moonstalker Sire[/url]s and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=2071]Moonstalker Matriarch[/url] drop the pelts. It is easier to kill the Sires because they do not have adds.\
 The Sires and Matriarchs can be found at 60,12 and 38, 80.\
 If you do this quest at 60,12, pair it with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=951]Mathystra Relics[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=2098]Gyromast's Retrieval[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=2078]Gyromast's Revenge[/url], Tower of Althalaxx ([url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=965]Part 1[/url]) and ([url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=966]Part 2[/url]).\
 If you do this quest at 38,80, pair it with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=1003]Buzzbox 525[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=948]Onu[/url] (and subsequent quests), and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=729]The Absent-Minded Prospector[/url] (as well as subsequent quests).\
 Also, if you're lucky and do this quest at 38,80 you may run into the rare spawn [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=2172]Strider Clutchmother[/url].\
\
Also note:\
 This quest requires level eleven and potentially the completion of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=984]How Big A Threat?[/url]\
 This quest is available to all Alliance races: Draenei, Night Elf, Human, and Gnome all can acquire it.",
