    "2360143727111434432007/08/25 07:44:52EqweexTry talking to the stealthed NPC near the tower in the southern Westfall. She is standing next to one of the big trees north of it, easy to find.",
    "23605301730530172007/03/18 04:52:01hauretThis quest is definately soloable at level 20.\
