    "23609900811488922007/06/05 22:15:56YukonCorneliousYea, definitely DO NOT have to be level 24, I did this fairly easily at level 20.",
    "2360207782102077822007/12/26 18:35:28synsinatikThe easiest way to pickpocket the malformed defias drone is to sap him first, then pick his lil pockets.",
    "23605279611488922007/03/17 17:58:21deathscythehPicked him no problem at level 21...March 17, 2007",
    "236020194190201942007/01/11 10:26:13pariversFirst talk to agent stealthed at 3rd tree north of the tower. She's on the west side of the big tree in front of the two little trees.  She will have the yellow \"?\" above her head.  She gives you a book with helpful hints, but I didn't use them.\
\
Then pickpocket the Malformed Lev24 Defias guard for the key.  He patrols around the tower and is often alone, just wait for opportunity.\
\
Enter tower in stealth mode. \
Up one level is a guard stationed in center of pathway.  Try to sneak passed her by walking up on the railing to the right (wait for patroling guard to be away). \
\
Even if you alert her, keep going to the right to next landing up.  She will follow but you can easily kill her without alerting patrol guard.  Stealth your way passed dual patrol on 3rd floor and make your way to top floor. \
\
Circle around to the right, chest is on floor near desk.  Sap the boss, the open chest - take book - make a hasty getaway. Or wait for the boss to walk away from the table. Open the box and then restealth. You can jump to first floor and run out - hopefully no guards patrolling out front, or stealth out again.\
\
The poison is easy enough to cure.  As directected talk to Doc in cellar of Barracks. Make sure you type \"/lay\" infront of him.\
\
