\
With my lvl 16 Druid, pulled two cubs killed them, then rest with swipe mostly. Casted regrowth before. Good luck!",
    "213913475011655022007/08/09 04:53:17koluchfigured how to solo her as 17 rogue after 1 death\
\
you stealth in, backstab the cub, gouge den mother, and start running back using sinister strike on injured cub. cub dies you get away.\
\
repeat until no cubs are left. \
\
finish off the den mother.",
    "2139146315101463152007/08/29 23:59:59BrighidFor some reason, I just couldn't seem to pull the cubs alone.\
\
So, on my 17 Druid, here is what I did.\
\
Get full health, put on all buffs.  Get as close as possible without aggroing (you can almost get right next to the first cub).  Cast Regrowth and Rejuvenation, blast the mother with Moonfire, then go into Bear Form and start attacking her.  Use Demoralizing Roar and Bash (on her) to help lessen incoming damage.  Keep using Maul as often as possible, and as soon as she dies, turn around and run straight out of the cave and jump off the hill.  Keep going until you leave combat.\
\
I should mention that the fall from the hill will do some damage and may kill you if you're very low on health.  Try to go slightly off to the left side before jumping; it's a shorter distance down in that spot.\
\
I did this as Balance; someone specced for Feral could kill her more quickly and get out sooner.  It's possible that you may get unlucky and be \"stunlocked\" by the bears.  If you see that you're at about 30% and the mother isn't nearly dead, try to run out so you can try again.\
\
It can be difficult, but it's rewarding when you pull it off!  Good luck!",
    "2139125107101251072007/07/22 18:13:32KevinHawkins[Hunter - lvl 15]\
[Pet - Cat lvl 15]\
No Death Solo\
Stuff used: One Lesser Healing Potion\
\
Pulled first two cubs, killed 'em. Then sent the pet in to target the mum. When he made contact, I started nuking the mum. Unfortunately the Growl was resisted, so I Concussive Shot and Arcane Shot the mum as she run towards me. Run back and sent the pet for her. She aggroed to him, but I had those two cubs up my neck. So I drank the potion, helped the pet kill the mum, then we killed the two remaining cubs.\
\
Somehow like this, perhaps not exactly :) The strategy, however, was to pull two of the cubs first and then when they are dead nuke the mum and see what happens.\
\
Good luck :)\
\
Kikki of Drak'Thul",
