    "1716140241201402412007/08/18 18:33:58bEwaReHm, I'm doing this quest as i write... I've got one idea that i'm going to try out. I'm playing on PVP server and normaly i died... And the thing is 2 horde chars were camping on my corpse. And i was tired of waiting them to go, so i released my spirit and started walking toward Barrens :) . I think you get my idea now ;)\
