    "1716200701111396842007/12/13 12:18:15brasshopperWestfall and Booty Bay coords are on different systems. I have tried to swim south along the coast in the Eastern Kingdom - from Menethil Harbor south, and I just ended up in a \"Dead Zone\" that never ended, and if I got more than a short way from the repeating coastline, I got \"fatigue\".\
