    "1716151358211100452007/09/10 16:50:52rellex... yes, their first step is to talk to someone in the same room, the second step is to kill a level 20 mob in silverpine that is difficult to solo pull (adds are 18ish) and a level 21 mob in WETLANDS that means they have to run from silverpine...thru hillsbrad, thru arathi, and across the thandol span... you mention possibly dying from horde problems...they WILL die from level 30 mobs and players, because they don't even have the option of not taking the road",
    "171613908651613752007/08/16 17:07:38aigganHere's what I think is the fastest way.... from Menthil go to Theramore via ship. Once in Theramore, head up the eastern coast past all the lvl 36ish turtles till you get to the Murlocks. I forget what level they are but they will appear ?? to a lvl 20. Turn on your water breathing ability and start swimming. (take off your gear just in case!)\
\
Stay away from the islands as there are murlocs on them. I swam between the islands and did not agro any of them. I stayed deep underwater but surfaced once close to Witch Hill and did not agro any.\
\
Luckily the only things I saw under water were non-agressive turtles. If you do it right you will end up by Northwatch Hold. It is smooth sailing to Rachet from there to get the flight path or just go straight to Takar the Seer if you want get the FP later.",
