    "6001181414101814142007/11/09 09:47:49RinorJust run out after you spawn it, root the mob and run back in the cave, spam Wrath and a Moonfire when roots wear off. For me roots didn't break so it died once it reached me melee... not hard, you just make it sound hard guys. :P",
    "600138126150381262007/02/18 12:03:26iamgreyas Zodin commented here: http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=12138#z0z Lunaclaw seems to be much easier than the mobs outside. When summoned, Lunaclaw will not aggro the other mobs, so there is no need to clear. You can run into the cave, take the death from the other mobs, it's a relatively short run from the graveyard. Rez on the stone, be sure to buff yourself like I forgot to do, and summon Lunaclaw. \
